nodes.text: The cousin of the human Fawn was a female musician. Around 31 ABY, she came from the Core Worlds planet Coruscant to visit the Outer Rim planet Batuu, and farmer Julen Rakab developed feelings for her. His friends, musicians Fawn and Neelo, later teased him for his bad romantic decisions. Rakab recalled liking the cousin's music, but cut off further conversation about his love life.
Fawn's cousin was mentioned in A Crash of Fate, a 2019 young-adult novel written by Zoraida Córdova.
